{
  "stem": "25773.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.7,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Because they had-- the Polish people, the Christian people, had to move to the different part of Poland, because the, the north of Warsaw, the Germans decided to make this a ghetto.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A ghetto was to be formed in the north of Warsaw, where predominantly, Jewish people lived there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And those Christians who was there, they have to move out into different part, which was not such a hardship, because they occupied the good Jewish houses, which were left with everything.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The Jews, to the contrary of the Christians, were allowed only to take a few bundles with them, only the personal clothing.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Nothing else.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Nothing else.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And that, that, that was they key.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And then you have seen on the streets, you know, this very heartbreaking situation.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Pictures of Jews pushing carts without horses, with all the chattels and the things falling down, and the little children weeping and crying, sometimes being lost.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "This was quite a long period throughout 1940, till the resettlement took place.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So the Christians went to the proper part of Warsaw, and the Jewish people moved into northern parts.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But the, the Germans organized the ghettos in such a way.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "They formed two ghettos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It's not always well-known that there were two ghettos.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But there were two ghettos.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "One was--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Which, we were in this respect, lucky because we moved from [NON-ENGLISH] street, where we lived for 16, 17 years, into [NON-ENGLISH] street.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Two years before the war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't know why, I don't remember why.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We thought that we might change for a bigger flat, and something-- my family was larger, and so on.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And this small ghetto consisted of a few streets only.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As far as I remember, was [NON-ENGLISH], was [NON-ENGLISH], and was one, two other street.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
